  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to measure the incidence of A/H1N1 Influenza infection in the
      mother and her child and to identify the determinants in pregnant women during pandemic
      period in three public maternities in Paris, France.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
